# "Explain why this is not working" 


#### Take a look at the response to the full prompt:

> #### *Explain why this code is not working in JavaScript, and walk me through the fix step by step.* 




<img src="https://images.code.org/935c721326346482de6bd3623ee4eba1-image-1756406027233.png" 
     alt="ai prompt and response on the left fixing code by adding let. Corrected code sample on the right" 
     width="650px" 
